// 1. Go to https://emailjs.com → sign up free
// 2. Add Email Service (connect Gmail) → copy SERVICE_ID
// 3. Create Template A — staff notification:
//      Subject: "New Counselling Appointment Request – {{student_name}}"
//      To Email: {{to_email}}   Reply-To: {{reply_to}}
//      Body: use all {{variables}} below as you like
// 4. Create Template B — student confirmation:
//      Subject: "We received your counselling request"
//      To Email: {{student_email}}
// 5. Account → API Keys → copy PUBLIC_KEY
// 6. Fill in the four constants below, then run:  npm install @emailjs/browser
